  "title": "12 Months Office Admin (Bank)  #NJN",
  "description": "<p><strong>12 Months Contract</strong><br /><strong>Labrador Park –</strong> <strong>shifting to Punggol in July 2026</strong><br />9AM to 6.30PM Monday to Thursday, and 9AM to 5.30PM Friday with 1 Hour meal break </p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>Perform the role of GBT Administrator; work closely with line managers on all administrative matters<br />Manage onboarding and offboarding activities for GBT, including system access, asset governance and tracking of laptops, seats and related resources<br />Process job requisitions in Workday and handle ad hoc requests<br />End to end management of resource details, headcount numbers, budgets and allocations across all GBT departments<br />Manage and sort group administrative mailbox<br />Manage PPM system and generate reports such as monthly management reports<br />Ensure process documentation is organised, updated and maintained regularly<br />Support projects and transformation initiatives when required<strong>\n</strong><br /><u><strong>Requirements </strong></u></p><ul><li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel including VLOOKUP and running macros</li><li>Proficient in PowerPoint for presentation and report creation</li><li>Comfortable running reports across platforms such as PEMS, SAP, PPM, JIRA, QLIK and others</li></ul><p><br />Jessica Nguyen Huynh Thanh Truc</p><p>CEI Reg. No. R23113787</p><p>EA License No. 99C4599</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p></p>",
